runs.comm: on a length and angling down the leg side, off the pad for a leg bye..
length ball, on middle and leg, clips to square leg
short and wide outside off, cuts it off the back foot to wide of backward point..
length ball on middle, pushes to backward point..
touch short outside off, pushes to cover
comes down the track to slog this short of a length ball, this was touch slowish and he was completely beaten. It straightens enough and goes past the swinging bat and hits the stumps..
tucks this to long leg
gets behind the lien to block it..
on a length and outside off, gets an outside edge which flies to wide of vacant slip region
length ball on middle, pushes to mid-on

what a ball! Superb one, absolute delight to watch that from a fast bowler. This was short and rises touch extra around the off stump and holding its line. Ilyas looks to block but ends up edging it and that was a must play line. Ilyas thought it came off the arm, very hard to tell though, but needs to walk back as umpire thought he nicked it..
tucks it to the leg side for a single..
over-steps as this been nicely worked away through backward of square leg
short ball on off stump, beaten but wide..
took it on the pad as he tries to clip it down through leg side..
gets on the top of the bounce and taps it to wide of backward point
shortish once again on the leg, edges it towards the keeper..
back of a length ball straying on the pads, tucks it to long leg
back of a length and moving across, waits and runs it to wide of third man for a boundary..
back of a length on the hips, off the thigh pad for a leg bye..
short and wide outside off, cuts it off the back foot but picks point fielder ..
length ball and angling down the leg side, helps that away to wide of shortish fine leg..
pushes at a away going length ball, beaten..
on a length and outside off, slashes it towards the cover region..
drifting down the leg, clips the pad..
pushes this length ball towards short cover..
slogs this shortish ball down to deep square leg, not able to timed that..
gets down and sweeps this length ball through backward of square leg
goes for a mighty heave to a flat length ball outside off, beaten
clip this to wide of deep backward square leg..
back of a length on off stump, pushes with soft hands infront of cover region
slogs this length ball down to deep square leg
short of a length on middle, defends
this one rises touch extra and zips across beating the outside edge..
length ball moving across from the leg stump, clears the front leg and goes for a hoick, ends up with a leading which lands into the safe hands of Raza at cover point.
touch short on off, defends it back towards the bowler

short of a length on the middle and off, this one moves away with good bounce. Ahmed stays in the crease and tries for a late dab, ends up with an edge back to the keeper. The bounce did the trick there..
bottom edge towards the slip, no harm done..
good length ball on off, defends by staying in the crease..
on a length and outside off, pushes infront of cover point..
back of a length straying on the pads, clips it to long leg for a single..
fullish delivery on off stump, clips it to wide of mid-on
short and wide outside off, cuts it off the back foot to sweeper cover..
bit of movement from outside off..
gets behind the line of this ball to block..
length ball around the off stump, lofts it down to wide of long-off, the mis-hit saved him..
short of a length ball on off stump, punches it back past the bowler and gets a boundary
full toss down leg, clips that to wide of deep square leg for a couple..
length ball holds the line outside off, slogs that nicely to deep midwicket fence..
length delivery moves away from outside off, left alone..
good length ball just shade outside off, pushes it infront of cover
length ball outside off, punches it between the gap at cover and point
ranks out a full toss on middle, clips it through square leg
length ball straightens on middle and leg, clips it to on side..

length ball which holds the line outside off stump. Mehran clears the front leg and tries to clear the man at long-on, not enough power onto it as the fielder ran across to his left and slips but manages to hold that flat catch on the slide. Very nicely done by Qadeer
back of a length on middle, tucks it away through square leg
full ball angling down the leg, clips the pad and rolls to on side..
length ball once again drifting on the pads, clips it to long leg
fullish and on the off stump, pushes towards cover..
pushes this across of the leftie from a length, beaten as he gets forward to drive that ball..
short ball, arm ball, defended off the back foot
flat and short on the leg, clips it around the corner for a single
drags this touch short and drifted down leg, called wide..
short and outside off, cuts it off the back foot down to deep point
gets down for a slog sweep, turns across to beat the bat..
once again he can't connect a length ball which was turning across from off..

and Raza strikes, another wicket gone and the parade is about to end..This was short and turns back in from wide of the crease. He goes back and tries to cut it, was too close for it and also kept quite low. The ball beats his bat and hits the timber...
clips this short of a length ball through square leg
gets on the top of the bounce and works it towards third man
pokes at length ball outside off and is beaten..
length ball outside off, punches it through backward point
pokes a shortish ball which was shaping across, beaten..
pushes this length ball towards cover point..
short and outside off, cuts it off the back foot to deep backward of point
gets behind the line of this short ball, pushes to leg side..
clips the pad on its way to the keeper
pushes quicker and straighter outside off, beats everyone and races away to the fence..
flat and straightish length ball, defends
short and way outside off, beaten..
length ball down leg, gets down touch and helps that way to wide of shortish fine leg..
short and wide outside off, cuts it off the back foot but finds backward point
runs this short ball with an open face to third man
short of a length and moves across, batsman was squared up and is beaten
length ball outside off, strides forward and driven down to sweeper for a single..
taps it from the crease to backward point..
this one kept low from a shortish length, defends..
length ball on off stump, blocks it once again..
pushes at a away going back of a length ball, beaten
short of a length ball, hits the arm and rolls to off side as he can't connect that with the bat..
once again beaten outside off, length ball moves across and the away movement was good enough to beat the edge..
short of a length, gets on the top of the bounce to defend..
clears the front leg and slogs this length ball down to deep midwicket
gets an outside edge to a shortish ball to wide of first slip and races away to the fence..
full ball and outside off, lifted it nicely over the mid-off and gets a boundary
short once again and down leg, swivels and works this down to long leg ..
punches this length ball around the carpet to long-off
gets the bat pad together to block this length ball..
length ball on the leg, clips it to short midwicket
short ball on the leg stump, mistimes the pull as he took his eyes off, top edges it down to long leg
short of a length on the leg, defends off the back foot..
pushes at a away going length ball, beaten
gets on the top of the bounce to this short ball and taps to point
back of a length moving across from off, beaten as he tries to steer it down to third man..
driven this full ball to wide of extra cover for a boundary
gets down touch and powers this shortish ball to wide of long-on and gets it over the fence, superb stroke..
full ball angling down the leg, clips the pad as he misses out..
short and wide outside off, cuts it off the back foot to point for a single..
yorker length ball on the leg, clips it out to midwicket

and finally he holes out, Zeeshan Maqsood gets onto the back foot and tries to cut this short ball, it hurries him touch. He was not able to pick the gap and also it came off the top edge which finds the safe hands of Kaleem at shortish third man..
punches this short ball to off side.
pushes full and quicker outside off, gets down to sweep and is beaten..
comes down the track for a big hoick, took it on the pad..
beaten outside off as he tries to pushes a length ball
clips this length ball towards square leg for a single
tossed up delivery outside off, lofts it down towards long-off
pushes full and outside off, beaten..
another quicker full ball outside off, beaten for the second time..
another one, pushes quick from round the wicket, can't put bat..
slogs this length ball down towards deepish midwicket for a single..
gets the bat pad together to block this length ball..
once again stretches forward and blocks it..
